<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="task-n">task <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /tɑːsk/    美 /tæsk/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>工作；任务</strong></h4>
<p>a piece of work that has to be done, especially an unpleasant or difficult one：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>a simple</strong> / hard / challenging <strong>task</strong> 
简单的/艰巨的/具有挑战性的任务</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>undertake a task</strong> 
承担任务</p></div></div>